front.title: All Power To Weapons
front.gametext: USED: If a battle was just initiated, each of your TIEs present is power +2 and immune to attrition for remainder of turn.  LOST: Lose 1 Force to take up to three non-unique TIEs into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: The TIE fighter's energy management system allows its pilot to transfer all power from engines to weapons at a moment's notice.
